A Lunatic Is Loose Among Us!: An escaped killer is on the loose.
Un-Lucky Horseshoe: "Lucky" Lee counts on his good luck charms to help him rob a house.
Death Is a Dummy in Disguise: Mitch Randall pins a murder on Davy Hoke, but Davy comes back from the grave to set things right.
Monstrosity!: Larry decides to get rich mining uranium.
